suscribirse (a algo) verb—

subscribe to sth. v (often used)

subscribe v (subscribed, subscribed) (often used)

Los usuarios pueden suscribirse al boletn en el sitio web. — Users can subscribe to the newsletter on the website.

sign up v (signed, signed)

La estudiante se suscribi al boletn informativo. — The student signed up for the newsletter.
less common:
sign up for sth. v
register v
